16112" class="brightcove"><div class="brightcove__holder lazyloaded"><div id="video_6347629716112_5067014667001-9197" class="brightcove__video video-js vjs-paused vjs-controls-enabled vjs-touch-enabled vjs-workinghover vjs-v7 vjs-user-active vjs-layout-medium bc-player-default_default bc-player-default_default-index-0 vjs-ad-controls vjs-ima3-html5 vjs-dock vjs-plugins-ready vjs-player-info vjs-errors vjs-parsely vjs-thumbnails vjs-tealium not-hover" lang="en-gb" tabindex="-1" role="region" translate="no" data-embed="default" data-video-id="6347629716112" data-application-id="Inline" data-brightcove-id="video_6347629716112_5067014667001-9197" data-video-id-pending="6347629716112" data-player="default" data-account="5067014667001" aria-label="Video Player" aria-labelledby="video_6347629716112_5067014667001-9197 vjs-dock-title-1" aria-describedby="vjs-dock-description-2">
<p>She also touched on her collab track ‘Free’ with <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/calvin-harris">Calvin Harris</a> , which was released back in July. “We just understand each other and it’s easy. I don’t take that for granted because being in the studio with people for the first time is like having a first date, basically,&#8221; shesaid.</p>
<p>She and Harris joined forces last year to release chart-topping hit ‘ <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/calvin-harris-ellie-goulding-new-collaboration-single-miracle-listen-3411368">Miracle</a> ’, which the latter said at the time marked the completion of a “trilogy” of tunes between the two, following 2012’s ‘I Need Your Love’ and 2014’s ‘Outside’.</p>
